channel.description:
[b]Credits: [/b]Lin
Just a heads up ;D
Okay. Some of my friends have been requesting this from me, so I decided to re-release it. If any of you leech it, remember the Perm ban from The Un-Named and a no more list releasing from me. It's not completely correct, because I only used the Global Objects, Floor objects, and doors, walls, etc... Orientations Meaning the Nothings aren't correct :)
Well, enjoy :D
Attached at the bottom.
